  "body_html": "<h2 id=\"xCO1c\">样本容量的确定</h2><p>样本量到底取多少合适？</p><h4 id=\"BBlSU\">估计总体均值时</h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/a94e8189f661958b74ed129f0f310f34.svg#card=math&amp;code=n%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Csigma%5E%7B2%7D%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D&amp;height=49&amp;width=110\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 110px;\" /></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">其中 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/521db5fd37a50eafaedfb1fbf02e3885.svg#card=math&amp;code=E%3Dz_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%20%5Cfrac%7B%5Csigma%7D%7B%5Csqrt%7Bn%7D%7D&amp;height=42&amp;width=96\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 96px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><blockquote><p>Q：经济学本科毕业生年薪的标准差大约为 2000 元，假定想要估计年薪 95% 的置信区间，希望边际误差为 400 元，应抽取多大的样本容量？</p><p><br /></p><p>A：</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/0002c7d55737b691db8fe0f1f10f506e.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Cbegin%7Barray%7D%7Bl%7D%7Bn%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Csigma%5E%7B2%7D%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B%281.96%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ctimes%202000%5E%7B2%7D%7D%7B400%5E%7B2%7D%7D%7D%20%20%7B%3D96.04%20%5Capprox%2097%7D%5Cend%7Barray%7D&amp;height=45&amp;width=304\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 304px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>所以应抽取 97 人。</p></blockquote><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"ikSoD\">估计总体比例时</h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/3349e11e3b101f24ccae9c97494e71ec.svg#card=math&amp;code=n%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ccdot%20%5Cpi%281-%5Cpi%29%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D&amp;height=49&amp;width=167\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 167px;\" /></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">其中误差 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/64b9dc2414b6ea891d90aab34d90a75b.svg#card=math&amp;code=E%3Dz_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%20%5Csqrt%7B%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpi%281-%5Cpi%29%7D%7Bn%7D%7D&amp;height=56&amp;width=151\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 151px;\" /></p><p>E 的取值一般小于 0.1</p><p>π 未知时，可取最大值 0.5</p><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"kcaGU\">估计两个总体均值之差时</h4><ul><li>n1 和 n2 位来自两个总体的样本，n1=n2</li><li>根据均值之差的区间估计公式可得两个样本的容量 n 为</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/f86a693c68c768348fea0f9e5f71e7d2.svg#card=math&amp;code=n_%7B1%7D%3Dn_%7B2%7D%3Dn%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ccdot%5Cleft%28%5Csigma_%7B1%7D%5E%7B2%7D%2B%5Csigma_%7B2%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright%29%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D&amp;height=49&amp;width=257\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 257px;\" /></p><ul><li>其中 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/a954fd5b256ce32a267971ea33d42627.svg#card=math&amp;code=E%3Dz_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%20%5Cfrac%7B%5Csigma_%7B1%7D%2B%5Csigma_%7B2%7D%7D%7B%5Csqrt%7Bn%7D%7D&amp;height=44&amp;width=127\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 127px;\" /></li></ul><p><br /></p><blockquote><p> Q：一所中学的教务处想要估计实验班和普通版考试成绩平均分数差值的置信区间。要求置信水平为 95%，预先估计两个班考试分数的方差分别为：实验班<span> </span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/c0fceb2937b8c8bec9a1b391b50aa488.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Csigma_%7B1%7D%5E%7B2%7D%3D90&amp;height=24&amp;width=57\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 57px;\" /><span>，普通班 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/31d87f49a9c57eb5646c15788551f07b.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Csigma_%7B2%7D%5E%7B2%7D%3D120&amp;height=24&amp;width=66\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 66px;\" /><span>。如果要求估计的误差范围（边际误差）不超过 5 分，在两个班应该分别抽取多少个学生？</span></span></p><p><span><span><br /></span></span></p><p><span><span>A：已知 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/a20986ec18afe047b9c8043ee37e426f.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Csigma_%7B1%7D%5E%7B2%7D%3D90%2C%20%5Cquad%20%5Csigma_%7B2%7D%5E%7B2%7D%3D120%2C%20%5Cquad%20E%3D5%2C%20%5Cquad%201-%5Calpha%3D95%20%5C%25%2C%20%5Cquad%20z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%3D1.96&amp;height=26&amp;width=443\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 443px;\" /></span></span></p><span><span><br /></span></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/a5e9c0324e89de73c2851dec1be30103.svg#card=math&amp;code=%5Cbegin%7Baligned%7D%20n_%7B1%7D%20%26%3Dn_%7B2%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ccdot%5Cleft%28%5Csigma_%7B1%7D%5E%7B2%7D%2B%5Csigma_%7B2%7D%5E%7B2%7D%5Cright%29%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D%20%5C%5C%20%26%3D%5Cfrac%7B1.96%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ctimes%2890%2B120%29%7D%7B5%5E%7B2%7D%7D%20%5C%5C%20%26%3D32.269%20%5Capprox%2033%20%5Cend%7Baligned%7D&amp;height=121&amp;width=230\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 230px;\" /></p></blockquote><p><br /></p><h4 id=\"chXgt\">估计两个总体比例之差时</h4><ul><li>n1 和 n2 位来自两个总体的样本，n1=n2</li><li>根据比例之差的区间估计公式可得两个样本的容量 n 为</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/d902bfb6dc12bab1df1a026bd52ee2cb.svg#card=math&amp;code=n_%7B1%7D%3Dn_%7B2%7D%3Dn%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ccdot%5Cleft%5B%5Cpi_%7B1%7D%5Cleft%281-%5Cpi_%7B1%7D%5Cright%29%2B%5Cpi_%7B2%7D%5Cleft%281-%5Cpi_%7B2%7D%5Cright%29%5Cright%5D%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D&amp;height=49&amp;width=377\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 377px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><p>其中估计误差 <img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/5a7a947d098985750ebb1c5a3a2f34af.svg#card=math&amp;code=E%3Dz_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%20%5Cfrac%7B%5Cpi_%7B1%7D%5Cleft%281-%5Cpi_%7B1%7D%5Cright%29%2B%5Cpi_%7B2%7D%5Cleft%281-%5Cpi_%7B2%7D%5Cright%29%7D%7B%5Csqrt%7Bn%7D%7D&amp;height=49&amp;width=253\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 253px;\" /></p><p><br /></p><blockquote><p>Q：分别在广告投放前和广告投放后抽取了两组样本，看看是否提升了知名度。相以 10%的误差范围，95%的置信水平估计两组数据的比例之差。应该分别抽取多少人？</p><p><br /></p><p>A：<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/3bdd26eb365c2cdce0276a3092f8b35c.svg#card=math&amp;code=E%3D10%20%5C%25%2C%20%5Cquad%201-%5Calpha%3D95%20%5C%25%2C%20%5Cquad%20z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%3D1.96&amp;height=26&amp;width=294\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 294px;\" /></p><p>由于没有总体比例 π 的信息，因此取 0.5。</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/__latex/73940f9f5db1843ac25ae6e9f0416a60.svg#card=math&amp;code=n_%7B1%7D%3Dn_%7B2%7D%3D%5Cfrac%7B%5Cleft%28z_%7B%5Calpha%20%2F%202%7D%5Cright%29%5E%7B2%7D%20%5Ccdot%5Cleft%5B%5Cpi_%7B1%7D%5Cleft%281-%5Cpi_%7B1%7D%5Cright%29%2B%5Cpi_%7B2%7D%5Cleft%281-%5Cpi_%7B2%7D%5Cright%29%5Cright%5D%7D%7BE%5E%7B2%7D%7D%3D192.08%E2%89%88193&amp;height=49&amp;width=463\" style=\"max-width: 600px; width: 463px;\" /></p></blockquote><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
